title: Sioux City Community School District
text: Sioux City Community School District (SCCSD) is a <a href="state%20school">public</a> <a href="school%20district">school district</a> headquartered in the Educational Service Center in <a href="Sioux%20City%2C%20Iowa">Sioux City, Iowa</a>. The district is mostly in <a href="Woodbury%20County%2C%20Iowa">Woodbury County</a>, with a portion in <a href="Plymouth%20County%2C%20Iowa">Plymouth County</a>.
